Yi Ran, what do you think of Tang San?

128
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:44,870
Grandpa, are you pairing us together?

129
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:48,010
If Little San carries on,

130
00:21:48,010 --> 00:21:49,700
he may be in danger.

131
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:51,470
Do you think

132
00:21:51,470 --> 00:21:54,880
Little San’s Martial Soul is only Blue Silver Plant?

